> - **Senses** passive Perception 16
> - **Languages** understands Celestial, Common, and Elvish but cannot speak
> - **Challenge** 1 (1100 XP)
> ___
> ***Major Image.*** The Pegasus can cast Major Image on itself to hide its wings and appear to be a normal war horse. The Pegasus cannot use this feature for any other purposes, but the effect lasts for 1 hour instead of 10 minutes.
>
> ***Multiattack.*** The Pegasus makes two Hooves attacks.
>
